Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:06.06,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}Drawn by a landscape as white as snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:12.61,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}I'm headed toward an unseen world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:21.54,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I've been traveling while lost
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.33,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Under this gray sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:30.42,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Every day with new maps, stained with my many dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.80,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I wonder if someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:36.84,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Even with these tiny steps of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:42.93,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I'll be able to travel beyond those clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.56,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I put on a bold front.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.10,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}End up hurting myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:49.19,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I feel empty inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.73,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's started to rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.90,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And the raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:56.11,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Began to repeat their scattered reflections.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:58.99,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}These straight rays of light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:01.70,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Start to cross one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:05.29,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}And without telling anyone where they're headed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.58,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Across the endless distances,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.17,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They pass through all matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:14.01,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I burn these faint afterimages onto my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.92,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Under this sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.72,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,450)}Wherever I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.06,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}I should be able to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:26.85,OP02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}The unseen world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:06.06,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)}{\blur3}真っ白な景色にいま誘われて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:12.61,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}僕は行くよ　まだ見ぬ世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:21.54,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}迷子のまま旅していた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.33,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}鼠色の空の下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:30.42,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}日替わりの地図 いくつもの夢が滲んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.80,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}いつかはさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:36.84,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}ちっぽけな僕のこの歩幅でも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:42.93,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}あの雲の向こうまで行けるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.56,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}強がって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.10,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}キズついた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:49.19,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}心透かしたように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.73,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}降り出した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.90,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雨粒たちが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:56.11,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}乱反射繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:58.99,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}真っ直ぐな光が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:01.70,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}交差して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:05.29,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}行き先も告げぬまま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.58,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.17,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}突き抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:14.01,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}淡い残像　両目に焼きつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.92,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}この空の下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.72,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,450)}どんなとこにいても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.06,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}届くはずなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:26.85,OP02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}まだ見ぬ世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:06.06,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}Masshiro na keshiki ni ima sasowarete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:12.61,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,450)}Boku wa yuku yo mada minu sekai e
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:21.54,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Maigo no mama tabi shiteita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.33,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Nezumiiro no sora no shita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:30.42,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Higawari no chizu ikutsumo no yume ga nijindeita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.80,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Itsuka wa sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:36.84,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Chippoke na boku no kono hohaba demo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:42.93,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Ano kumo no mukou made yukeru kana
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.56,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tsuyogatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.10,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kizutsuita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:49.19,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Kokoro sukashita youni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.73,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Furidashita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.90,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Amatsubu tachi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:56.11,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Ranhansha kurikaesu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:58.99,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Massugu na hikari ga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:01.70,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kousa shite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:05.29,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Yakusaki mo tsugenumama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.58,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Doko made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.17,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tsukinukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:14.01,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Awai zanzou ryoume ni yakitsukete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.92,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kono sora no shita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.72,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,450)}Donna toko ni itemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.06,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(450,0)}Todoku hazu nanda
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:26.85,OP02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}Mada minu sekai e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:33.37,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,657)}{\fad(500,0)}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:37.46,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to act tough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:44.25,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scribbling someone made...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:50.05,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,On the wall, of a flower is swaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:55.64,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows their true selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.93,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we both lose and gain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:01.35,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,By embarking on this long, long path,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:09.03,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}And though there may be days loneliness strikes and makes us weep...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:16.54,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let's transform our tears and pains to stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:22.54,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let's light a candle to illuminate our tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:27.67,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll hold our small hands over the fire to create stardust,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:32.89,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,And an eternity that shines so brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:38.27,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewells may be unavoidable,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:44.19,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Yet the seasons continue to change obliviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:48.28,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I lose myself, I'll continue to walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:52.32,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:56.58,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}That's the only thing I'd like to never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:37.46,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,強がらなくていいんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:44.25,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,誰かが描いてった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:50.05,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,壁の落書きの花が　揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:55.64,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,自分らしさなんて, 誰もわからないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.93,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,長い長い道の途中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:01.35,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,失くしたり, 拾ったり,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:09.03,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}急に寂しくなって, 泣いちゃう日もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:16.54,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}涙も　痛みも　星に変えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:22.54,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}明日を照らす　灯りをともそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:27.67,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,小さな手かざして　ふたりで作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:32.89,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,星屑を　強く光る永遠を探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:38.27,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,さよなら　いつかは来るかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:44.19,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}季節はそれでも巡り巡ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:48.28,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,小さく迷っても　歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:52.32,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,君と歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:56.58,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}それだけは変わらないでいようね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:37.46,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyogaranakute iindane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:44.25,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Dareka ga kaitetta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:50.05,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Kabe no rakugaki no hana ga yureru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:55.64,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Jibunrashisa nante dermo wakaranaiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.93,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagai nagai michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:01.35,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakushitari hirottari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:09.03,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Kyuu ni samishikunatte naichau hi mo arukedo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:16.54,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Namida mo itami mo hoshi ni kaeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:22.54,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ashita wo terasu akari wo tomosou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:27.67,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiisana te kazashite futari de tsukurou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:32.89,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshikuzu wo tsuyoku hikaru eien wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:38.27,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayonara itsuka wa kurukamoshirenai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:44.19,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Kisetsu wa soredemo meguri megutteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:48.28,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiisaku mayottemo aruiteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:52.32,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi to aruiteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:56.58,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}Sore dake wa kawaranaideiyoune
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:35.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Anyone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:39.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Al!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:41.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:43.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:45.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:47.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:48.75,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.34,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Is that any way to speak to a prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:01.60,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're not actually Envy disguised as Lin, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.35,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:10.27,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to recite the entire room service menu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you're not fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:15.90,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a fake either, are you? You pea--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:18.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a pea-sized runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:20.32,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:27.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:33.50,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, we were swallowed up by Gluttony, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:37.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but there's no way his stomach could be this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.09,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:41.80,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.31,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,It's the deserted house we were just in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.68,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:50.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The Lieutenant's car?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.57,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's safe to assume that all this fire came from the Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...we're really inside Gluttony's stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:02.95,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.49,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,But I can at least tell you we're not in Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:08.91,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:17.42,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Al's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:22.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If we can only find his arm,\Nthat means Al wasn't swallowed with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:28.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Al is worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no idea where we are, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:38.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the perfect time for them to awaken!\NMy telepathic abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:40.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Elric telepathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:43.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.16,Default-alt,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:53.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I see a lot of buildings and corpses,\Nbut they're all from different times...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.38,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Is there even an exit to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. And if there isn't, I'll make one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:01.17,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,And where are you going to make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All right, throw that stick in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.47,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I see what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.01,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's hit the bottom yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.99,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,A wall! Let's look for a wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:27.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! No matter how big the place is, we'll eventually reach the edge if we just keep moving forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:30.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to find the exit, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.58,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:40.67,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go, Shao May?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.63,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it got eaten up by a stray dog or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.88,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,A stray?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.89,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:50.89,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:56.85,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Shao May is a panda who has had a minor disorder since birth, which prevented her from getting any bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:00.90,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I found her after she was abandoned by her parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:04.74,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,...and we've been raised like sisters ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:14.41,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,My clan, the Chang, barely has any authority in Xing, making us one of the weakest clans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.00,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:24.76,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,How can I put it... we were both attracted to each other because of our similar standings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:30.18,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It may have been sympathy at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:47.28,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,...but we were raised like family, carried the same burdens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:52.49,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,...and she eventually became someone irreplaceable to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:01.38,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of things I was able to go through, just because she was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:05.76,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have been able to cross the desert without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.51,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you really had to cross it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:13.43,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do all this for something uncertain like immortality?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:19.60,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't bring back the method of immortality...\NIf I don't present it to the Emperor and earn his favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:22.77,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,My clan will die out at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.90,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came here with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.32,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,With her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:32.57,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Shao May!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.57,Default-alt,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.04,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.67,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,We still have some time before the sun rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:49.88,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be alot of military police on-duty at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:50.51,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.39,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,You'll help me look for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.48,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:02.98,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,His people died out in that civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:10.86,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe he's empathizing with you and your weak clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.83,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Aren't you going to look for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.25,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:28.92,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Having to walk in all this really drains your stamina, doesn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:33.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And no signs of an exit, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.81,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:44.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If we manage to get out, I'll let you eat all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:48.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Eat all you want, sleep all you want, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:51.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.07,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, giving up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:03.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You going to collapse here, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Get up! Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving you behind, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.09,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Then go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:18.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really going to go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Not joking, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.45,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you were going to go ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:41.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely don't want to die with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:45.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But you've got people waiting for you, too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:49.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you have the strength to talk, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.81,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,If only we had something to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:05.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know, Lin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:15.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Leather goods are edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Should be done by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.00,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have athlete's foot, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:28.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like I do, dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.34,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:38.01,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't tried to save me back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:39.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:43.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing compared to the training I went through as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of annoying we don't know where we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:51.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,but we can search for the exit now that we've had our beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.69,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,An optimist, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just relentless about staying alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:10:01.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I even thought about giving up,\NI'd get beaten and scolded by Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:05.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.50,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.46,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.75,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:15.80,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Envy, just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Please, tell us where the exit is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:20.93,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,That's pathetic, Edward Elric!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Humans would do anything to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.14,Default-alt,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.47,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.14,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,...there's no exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:24.76,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:25.47,Default-alt,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You're despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.52,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.31,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You really had to do that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:34.07,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Even I got dragged in because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.53,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.07,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really inside Gluttony's stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.82,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,We're inside his stomach, and at the same time, we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:44.70,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal ru-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:49.08,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Fullmetal Alchemist, shouldn't you have realized where we are by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\Nwhen I was sucked in by Gluttony...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I recognize that sensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.30,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.18,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Since you've gone through it in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The Gate of Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:15.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:18.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It was all white, and there was a gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:21.99,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's how the real one is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:22.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"Real"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:28.16,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony is the result of Father's unsuccessful attempt at recreating the Gate of Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What... did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:38.67,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,A poorly-made Gate of Truth that even Father couldn't get right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:43.43,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's safe to call this place the crevice between reality and the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The crevice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.81,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no exit, nor a way to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:52.89,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do now is to wait until\Nthe span of our lives comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:54.56,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:57.61,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,...is wait until we die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:09.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:12.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No way in hell I'll let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw around with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:15.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Envy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:16.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.46,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,There's no exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:21.76,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:31.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I die here, what will Al do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I promised him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:36.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I promised him we'd get our bodies back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:39.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:44.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is this Father guy that tried to recreate the Gate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Führer President Bradley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.99,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Bradley?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.33,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.33,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.58,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Research Laboratory 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Using people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:02.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Philosopher's stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:11.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If the Führer President is also a Homunculus, then that means it was you guys who started the Ishbal conflict...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:12.97,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Ishbal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.85,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,That was the most amusing task I'd ever been given!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:20.98,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what started that civil war in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:26.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, an army officer accidentally killed an Ishbalan child...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.53,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:32.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who shot the kid dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:57.73,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:03.23,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about Ishbal from Yoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.82,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,That felt amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:13.87,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Watching the civil war spread indefinitely from a single bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:17.37,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it was really refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.50,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:27.67,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I disguised myself as a moderate officer who was against the military intervention of Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:30.26,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Hear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:35.27,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't even give an excuse for it and was sentenced to death by court-martial!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:40.44,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are so easy to manipulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:44.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The one who shot an innocent child dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:53.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The one who destroyed our hometown... The one who drove away the Ishbalans...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The one who created Scar, a vengeful murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The root cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:02.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...of what killed Winry's parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:09.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.89,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't give an inch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.97,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You brats want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:16.72,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Ed, pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:25.11,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,We're all going to die here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:28.53,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you something cool as a final gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:32.95,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you look beneath his feet when you were fighting him in the woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:33.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:41.62,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,He may not look like it, but he weighs quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.21,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,His true form must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.85,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:04.10,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,How could that be a Homunculus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:07.19,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,An artificial human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.21,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:32.76,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,...should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.84,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.47,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do... I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.52,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get yelled at by Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:49.32,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Father? You have a dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.23,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.70,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The one who created the Homunculi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.61,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.66,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What happens to the mass you swallow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.42,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a trick to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Think... Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:11.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We decided we'd get our bodies back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.34,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:20.18,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony, take me to your Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:23.98,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:28.31,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,You're a human sacrifice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.32,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, that's right. I'm a human sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:36.40,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck does he mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:44.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones currently confirmed as such are the Elric brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.79,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,What about Doctor Marcoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.12,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,You would think that it's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.58,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,There's Kimblee, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:53.96,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have the nerve to open the Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:59.68,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what about Mustang, the other sacrifice candidate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:04.64,Default,Raven,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President wants to have a long chat with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:11.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you letting me live?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.11,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,To make you understand where you stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:20.11,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Since when has the military been beholden to the Homunculi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:25.04,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,It has been set up that way ever since this country was first reformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:29.87,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,So you've been smiling with glee, watching us struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:34.80,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands that were shaking during Brigadier General Hughes' funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Was that just an act?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:43.51,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone makes too big a deal out of the death of a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:49.64,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,They should have known his military uniform might become his burial attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:57.57,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Brigadier General Hughes' daughter was so annoying during the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:02.16,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,She really got on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.28,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, you also have a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:06.83,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.33,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you referring to Selim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:12.08,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:17.92,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how he'd react if he were to find out that his father, a man of utmost standing, is a Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.26,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to blackmail me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.30,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,It is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:28.18,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,He won't become my weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.19,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,But you're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:35.19,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,She'll become your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.07,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Hawkeye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.32,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:45.20,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from the personnel bureau dropped by earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:49.50,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,I was transferred to Southern Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.91,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:53.46,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Not just me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.42,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Breda was transferred to Western Headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:01.17,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,and Warrant Officer Falman was transferred to Northern Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.31,Default,Yako,0000,0000,0000,,You're Lieutenant Hawkeye, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.06,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.90,Default,Yako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yakovleff, from the personnel bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.65,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Personnel bureau...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:22.40,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shtolhi, an assistant to the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.36,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:27.37,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a transfer order?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.70,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.29,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to review it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.13,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:41.46,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What is with this insane personnel change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.01,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you assigned?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:48.89,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,"Starting tomorrow, Lieutenant Riza Hawkeye will be stationed at Central Headquarters..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.98,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,"...as an assistant to the Führer President."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.02,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.02,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Roy Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.45,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,How delightful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:11.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, this isn't delightful at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.79,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Not the least bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:20.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.38,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:32.22,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:34.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a sea of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:37.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty of iron here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:44.90,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You have bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:48.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How so? I think it looks cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:53.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.62,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:57.29,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:22:01.13,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,And to top it off, that earlier attack broke a few of my ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:03.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:08.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't be satisfied until I give him a good beatdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:17.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony, are you sure we're going the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:18.14,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.98,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But this way... we're headed toward...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:27.15,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Your Father is in Central?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:03.29,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Is the soul acting in the shadows a guidepost to the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:06.25,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fight, boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:10.38,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx96}if you are to see the truth and discover the depth of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:15.85,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.85,0:24:18.64,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 26, Reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:22.10,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say farewell...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:25.60,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...because I believe we'll meet again.
